    <div class="bit-60"> 
     <p class="intro-p">Visit Westmont and see one of the most beautiful campuses in the world. Our location in the foothills of scenic Santa Barbara offers stunning views of the Pacific Ocean and Santa Ynez mountains. We’d love to welcome you to our wooded acres and formal gardens. You’ll learn from world-class faculty and engaging students how Westmont can prepare you for a lifelong journey of spiritual growth, academic pursuit and personal maturity.</p> 
