     <h2>All Prospective Student Events</h2> 
     <h3>Personal Visit</h3> 
     <h5>Scheduling a Personal Visit:</h5> 
     <p>Schedule your visit to Westmont by using the link below or by contacting our visit coordinator at 1-(800)-777-9011 or by email <a href="mailto:visit@westmont.edu" class="maroon">visit@westmont.edu</a>. Please schedule your visit at least one week in advance.</p> 
     <table> 
      <tbody>
       <tr>
        <th>Tour Times</th> 
        <th>&nbsp;</th> 
       </tr>
       <tr> 
        <td class="first">M, W, F</td> 
        <td class="first">9 a.m., 11:30 a.m., 2 p.m., 4 p.m.</td> 
       </tr> 
       <tr> 
        <td>T, TH</td> 
        <td>9 a.m., 11 a.m., 2 p.m., 4 p.m.</td> 
       </tr> 
      </tbody>
     </table> 
     <p>You may also wish to meet with an admissions counselor in a session open to all visitors or in a personal interview (available for seniors and transfers).</p> 
