     <h3 class="scholars">Preview Days</h3> 
     <p>Fall Preview Days are a great opportunity to get to know Westmont College and learn more about the admission process. Each information-packed day will offer an in-depth look at academics, faith, and community at Westmont while giving you a chance to ask your questions about college life.</p> 
     <p><strong>Cost to attend:</strong> $25 per student (includes lunch in the Dining Commons and a Westmont t-shirt)</p> 
     <p><a href="/admissions/documents/fall-preview-days-schedule-2014.pdf" target="_blank" class="maroon">Schedule of Events</a></p> 
     <p><a href="/admissions/preview-day-details.html" target="_blank" class="maroon">Detailed Preview Day Info</a></p> 
     <p>Fall 2015 Preview Day dates will be posted this coming summer. Please see our other visit opportunities or schedule a personalized visit to campus. </p> 
