     <a id="spring"></a>
     <h3 class="spring">Spring Sessions</h3> 
     <p><strong>Come for college, launch for life.</strong></p> 
     <p>Want to get a taste of college life before your senior year? Excited to start the search for the right college? Curious about where to begin?</p> 
     <p>Westmont College Preview Days Spring Sessions are designed just for you!</p> 
     <p>Each spring session will help you discover what makes Westmont unique and provide helpful tips and hints as you begin this important next step in your education.</p> 
     <h5>Spring Session Highlights:</h5> 
     <ul class="list-indent bullets"> 
      <li>Learn about the history of Westmont on a campus tour</li> 
      <li>Experience Westmont's top-ranked academics as you sit in on a class</li> 
      <li>Join in worship with the Westmont community as you attend Chapel</li> 
      <li> Enjoy lunch in the Dining Commons</li> 
      <li>Hear more about the college search from our admission counselors</li> 
      <li>Discover what makes our Christian liberal arts education an affordable option</li> 
      <li>Interact with Westmont students</li> 
      <li>Explore beautiful Santa Barbara</li> 
     </ul> 
     <h5>Event Dates</h5> 
     <p>Beginning March 9, 2015 through April 24, 2015 on Monday, Wednesday and Fridays, our office will be hosting 1/2 day Spring Sessions (excluding Spring Break March 30th). Our last overnight ability to host is April 27.</p> 
     <p>Seniors and transfers: Are you considering Westmont but have not yet visited campus? We encourage you to schedule an individual visit <a href="http://webapps.westmont.edu/forms/admissions/visit_new/" target="_blank" class="maroon">tailored just for you</a>.</p> 
     <div class="btn">
      <a href="http://webapps.westmont.edu/forms/admissions/spring_pdays/" target="_blank"><img src="images/btn-register.png" alt="register button" width="50%"></a>
     </div> 
     <a id="move"></a>
     <h3 class="move">MOVE at Westmont</h3> 
     <p><strong> M.O.V.E. (Multicultural Overnight Visit Experience)</strong> - at Westmont is more than just another college visit. M.O.V.E.'s goal is to empower you with the confidence and plan to move toward a future that is truly fitted to your unique gifts and goals.</p> 
     <p>This is an opportunity to gain an in-depth view of college life as you sit in on a class, visit chapel, and stay overnight in the residence halls. In addition, M.O.V.E. will offer you time to interact with our faculty and staff from underrepresented and first-generation backgrounds as they share their stories with you. Come be a part of a fun weekend in Santa Barbara. Join us for M.O.V.E.! .</p> 
     <p>Event Date: April 17-18</p> 
     <div class="btn">
      <a href="https://secure.westmont.edu/forms/admissions/move/" target="_blank"><img src="images/btn-register.png" alt="register button" width="50%"></a>
     </div> 
     <p class="note"> Registration closes Monday, April 6</p> 
     <!--  <p class="note">Registration for this event is full. We invite you to attend one of our Spring Visit Sessions or schedule a personalized visit to campus by contacting our visit coordinator. </p>--> 
