    <div class="bit-60"> 
     <h2>Admitted Student Events</h2> 
     <h3 class="scholars">Scholars Weekend</h3> 
     <p><strong>Congratulations on your offer of admission to Westmont!</strong></p> 
     <p>Choosing a college is one of the most important decisions you’ll ever make, and we want to assist you in any way we can. Now that you've been admitted, you likely have thought of new questions to ask.</p> 
     <p>Westmont Scholars Weekend gives you an opportunity to get the information you need to choose a college. Look at Westmont through a different lens as you learn what it means to belong to this community academically, spiritually and socially.</p> 
     <p>During this special weekend, you’ll meet our internationally renowned faculty and explore our rigorous academics as you interact with Westmont students and experience life on campus.</p> 
     <p>Even if you’ve visited before, you may want to consider attending this event to take another look at what Westmont offers.</p> 
     <p><i>*This event is reserved for admitted Dean's, Provost's or President's scholars.</i></p> 
     <p><strong>Dates:</strong><br> Scholars Weekend - March 6-7, 2015</p> 
     <p><a href="/admissions/documents/scholars-weekend-schedule-2015.pdf" target="_blank" class="maroon">Tentative Schedule of Events</a></p> 
     <p><a href="/admissions/admitted-students-day-details.html" target="_blank" class="maroon">Detailed Scholars Weekend Info</a></p> 
     <!--   <div class="btn"><a href="https://secure.westmont.edu/forms/admissions/admitted_students/index.php?type=whw" target="_blank"><img src="images/btn-register.png" alt="register button" width="50%" /></a></div>
                     <p class="note"> Registration closes Monday, March 2</p>
               
                   <p> If you’re unable to attend our Scholars Weekend, you’re more than welcome to attend our April Admitted Student Days event.</p>
                   
                   --> 
     <p>Registration for Westmont Scholars Weekend has reached capacity and registration is closed at this time. We invite you to attend our April 10-11 Admitted Student Days or schedule a personalized visit to campus. If you have any questions, please contact Andrea Lashua at <a href="mailto:admissionevents@westmont.edu">admissionevents@westmont.edu</a>.</p> 
     <a id="admitted"></a>
     <h3>Admitted Student Days</h3> 
     <p><strong>Congratulations on your offer of admission to Westmont!</strong></p> 
     <p>Choosing a college in an important decision, and we’re here to help! </p> 
     <p> Whether you’ve visited campus before or you’re making your first trip, we invite you to pursue moments of discovery during Admitted Student Days and explore what Westmont offers academically, spiritually, and socially. </p> 
     <p>You won't want to miss it! </p> 
     <p><strong>Date of Event</strong><br> April 10-11, 2015</p> 
     <p><a href="/admissions/documents/admitted-student-tentative-schedule-2015.pdf" target="_blank" class="maroon">Tentative Schedule of Events</a></p> 
     <p><a href="/admissions/admitted-students-day-details.html" target="_blank" class="maroon">Detailed Admitted Student Day Info</a></p> 
